  :summary
"Book of Code authored end-to-end. 16 chapters + 8 appendices + cover
+ MANIFEST. 20,000-year arc from Ishango bone through electricity,
Boolean logic, gates, adders, memory, state machines, ALU, CPU,
memory hierarchy, assembly, OS, networks, and modern LLM ecosystem.
Every chapter runnable Motoi Scheme + ASCII diagrams. Petzold shape
(not text). LLM neutrality preserved: Claude, Gemini, OpenAI/GPT,
DeepSeek all get equal descriptive treatment. Ada cosign recommended
before v8 training fold."

